1. Only allow specific origins: `https://app.example.com` and `https://admin.example.com`
2. Support credentials (cookies) with `Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true`
3. Must echo the specific origin (not use `*`) when credentials are enabled
4. Include `Vary: Origin` to prevent cache poisoning
